e="abcb-glossentry">Performance Requirement</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1829_2.4.0.xml#_c78db730-5473-4624-a33f-2237c86f4944" id="_078e98e8-96fc-4b04-93c2-5404c0fa3710" scope="local" type="clause">H2P2</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1811_3.37.0.xml#_04e7d3da-0d06-4322-bf16-7b0c3830b0e0" id="_f100cece-96c7-4200-b67f-9459428f1e35" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">H1D8(1)</xref> only references AS 2047 for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1525_29.1.0.xml#_48631093-d96b-4a40-a86d-7ffae028f24d" id="_1ff6b9a3-577c-4322-a0cd-118432ef04e8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">windows</xref>. If AS 1288 is used for glazing in an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_94e8298d-4226-44a4-8df5-763713bb65b8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">external wall</xref>, it is still necessary to satisfy <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1829_2.4.0.xml#_c78db730-5473-4624-a33f-2237c86f4944" id="_a2e820e9-dc17-4240-8eb2-d11dbf3c8b6c" scope="local" type="clause">H2P2</xref>.</p></callout></clause>